dmca.title: DMCA notice to Google, Inc.
dmca.body:
Xi'an Diamond Network Co., Ltd.

ATTN: Google, Inc.
Google Legal Spport, DMCA Complaints 
1600 Amphitheatre Parkway
Mountain View, CA, 94043, USA
Fax: (650) 963-3255

FROM: Flora Niu
Youabc.com - Xi'an Diamond Network Co. Ltd.
Suite 511, Yu Yuan Mansion,No.65 Nan Er Huan XI Duan, 
Xi'an, Shaanxi, 710068, P.R.C.
Tel: (86-29) 8523 6688 Ext. 201
Fax' (86-29)85:9 7349
E-mail: dmca@youabc.com
DATE: March 28, 2007

Dear Google, Inc.

Thank you for your email of 28th March 2007. We appreciate your professional ability and patience during this process.

Sorry for my confusion, in my infringement complaint email dated February 15, 2007. I claimed that the two infringing pages www.517free.com/zh-cn/city/me/hh6.htm and
www.517free.com/zh-tw/city/mg/hh6.htm copied our copyrighted page
http://www.youabc.com/huhehaote/jiaotong/ like this:
"(64).Search Query: "[traditional Chinese characters]"
Our Copyrighted Page:
http://www.youabe.com/huhehaote/jiaotong/
Infringing Web Pages: (Except for a few words, nearly the whole article was copied from ours.)
www.517frec.com/zh-cn/hh.asp
www.5I7free.com/zh-tw/hh.asp (traditional Chinese characters version)
www.517free.com/zh-cn/city/mg/hh6.htm
www.517free.com/zh-ew;city/mg/hh6.htm (traditional Chinese characters version)"
I just mistook "hhb.htm" for "hh7.htm" due to my careless proofreading. As a result, you have not taken action on these two pages. So I want to trouble you to remove these two pages hereunder. 
www.517free.com/zh-en/city/mg/hh7.htm
www.517free.com/zh-tw/city/mg/hh7.htm

I assure you that there were not other mistakes in my infringement complaint letters except above-mentioned onc.

Please let me know if I can be of further assistance. Thank you very much!
Yours sincerely
Flora Niu
